Text:
This is most probably again a useless rar file with another password protected rar file in it, and they want you to click on ads again and again, but you never get the password, and the rar file contains nothing but garbage anyway.

Download at your own peril !

NOTE: This collection is not up to date! It contains NO server manuals after 2010. NONE of the 2011 and 2012 service manuals are in here. It's just the 2010 Service Manual torrent repackaged. The password IS "steve" as previously noted. Seems like this is just some jerks way of making money off of someone else's torrent (you do have to click through ads to get "steve")
